OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772910672
OL,3,CPolice use live facial recognition in
OL,4,CCumbria for first time
OL,6,FPolice have used live facial
OL,7,Frecognition (LFR) in Cumbria for the
OL,8,Ffirst time.
OL,10,FThe technology was deployed in the
OL,11,Fvicinity of Brunton Park for Carlisle
OL,12,FUnited's game against Southend United
OL,13,Fon Saturday (7 March).
OL,15,FIt allows officers to identify people
OL,16,Fwho are wanted by police, as well as
OL,17,Fthose who are subject to court orders.
OL,19,FThe LFR works by comparing faces
OL,20,Fcaptured on a live camera feed against
OL,21,Fa predetermined watchlist.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
