CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772910672
OL,3,CPolice use live facial recognition in
OL,4,CCumbria for first time
OL,6,FIf the system identifies a possible
OL,7,Fmatch, a police officer will compare
OL,8,Fthe image on screen with the person in
OL,9,Fview and decide whether to speak to
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,FIf a person passing the camera is not
OL,13,Fon a watchlist, their biometric data
OL,14,Fis not stored, and is immediately and
OL,15,Fautomatically deleted.
OL,17,FDetective Superintendent Dan St
OL,18,FQuintin from Cumbria Constabulary said:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
