PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772910672
OL,3,CPolice use live facial recognition in
OL,4,CCumbria for first time
OL,6,F"Live facial recognition is a scanning
OL,7,Fsystem, it's the first time we've used
OL,8,Fit in Cumbria. It essentially searches
OL,9,Ffor people in crowds that may be of
OL,10,Finterest to the police. That's either
OL,11,Fbecause they might be criminals intent
OL,12,Fon causing trouble, or actually
OL,13,Fsomeone who's really vulnerable who
OL,14,Fwe're looking for.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772910672
OL,3,CPolice use live facial recognition in
OL,4,CCumbria for first time
OL,6,F"People have got valid concerns about
OL,7,Ftheir privacy, but I'd just like to
OL,8,Freassure people that if they're not on
OL,9,Fany watchlist that we keep, their
OL,10,Fimage will be deleted within less than
OL,11,Fa second, automatically by the
OL,12,Fcomputer technology."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/4
